name: MyFavouriteCountryandNationalAnthem
0:
”Alexa open my favourite country”
”Alexa start my favourite country”
”help”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my favourite country
des:
You can select your favourite countries or say any country you like and listen to its national anthem.
Example: Alexa, what is my favourite country. 

You can select and listen to the anthems of the more than 175 countries.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
